channel.title: Golden Eagle Dev
channel.description: We are small team from Poland. Our main goal is to do fun games. First game that we developed is Maze Game: Cube. We released Fap and our latest game Tap Miner. Actually we are working on new arcade game "Galaxy Ball" and idle game "Donuts Clicker". We will tell you more soon!

item.title: Donuts Clicker news!
item.description: Donuts Clicker is in a half way done. We will share a trello list soon, so you will see the progress. Meantime you can subscribe to early-registration or play our other-games.
